==Amharic==
[[Category:Amharic language]]
===Noun===
'''ይሉኝታ''' (yiluññita)

#The inability to say "no"; caring about what others may think; [[consideration]] of others; swallowing one’s pride and doing what seems wrong in order not to offend; concern for public opinion; peer pressure. Literally: "What they tell me" (ይሉኝ ''yiluññ'') + nominal suffix "-ta". Contrasted with [[አለኝታ]], 'moral support' (lit. "What he told me".)

